com.starsoft.simpleandroidasynclibrary.executors.preinstal.base.threadpools

Class MultiThreadPool

  • com.starsoft.simpleandroidasynclibrary.executors.preinstal.base.threadpools.MultiThreadPool

  • public class MultiThreadPool

    Thread pool with a starting number of threads equal to the number of processors + 1 and a maximum number of threads equal to the number of processors * 2. This ThreadPool can connect to Lifecycle by com.starsoft.simpleandroidasynclibrary.core.lifeciclesupport.interfaces.LifecycleSupport.connectToLifecycle method
